We already set some of these in the toolchain, and the rest may conflict
with flags the user can set (like -fcf-protection vs -mindirect-brnanch=thunk).
--- a/meson.build
+++ b/meson.build
@@ -30,9 +30,7 @@ project('leancrypto', 'c',
